@startuml sequence-pembatalan-refund
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence Diagram — Pembatalan & Refund (Global)

actor Pelanggan
actor "Staff / Owner" as Staff
participant "Aplikasi Web" as App
participant "Backend API" as API
database "Database" as DB

== Skenario 1: Belum Terkonfirmasi / Belum Bayar ==

Pelanggan -> App : Buka detail booking
App -> API : GET /booking/{jenis}/{id}
API -> DB : SELECT booking + transaksi
DB --> API : status = MENUNGGU_KONFIRMASI / MENUNGGU_PEMBAYARAN
API --> App : Detail booking
App --> Pelanggan : Tampilkan tombol "Batalkan"

Pelanggan -> App : Klik batalkan booking
App -> API : PATCH /booking/{jenis}/{id}/batalkan
API -> DB : UPDATE booking status = DIBATALKAN
API -> DB : UPDATE transaksi status = DIBATALKAN
API -> DB : Kembalikan kuota (slot_terisi -1)
API -> DB : INSERT notifikasi BOOKING_DIBATALKAN
DB --> API : OK
API --> App : 200 OK
App --> Pelanggan : Notifikasi pembatalan berhasil

== Skenario 2: Sudah Terkonfirmasi & Sudah Bayar ==

Pelanggan -> App : Buka detail booking (status TERKONFIRMASI)
App --> Pelanggan : Tombol batalkan otomatis tidak tersedia\nTampilkan "Hubungi Kami"

Pelanggan -> App : Klik Hubungi Kami
App --> Pelanggan : Redirect ke wa.me/{PETSHOP_WHATSAPP}
note over Pelanggan, Staff
  Pelanggan sampaikan ID booking
  & alasan via WhatsApp (di luar sistem)
end note

Staff -> App : Buka dashboard internal
Staff -> App : Batalkan booking (permintaan WA)
App -> API : PATCH /internal/booking/{jenis}/{id}/batalkan
API -> DB : UPDATE booking status = DIBATALKAN
API -> DB : UPDATE transaksi status_refund = PENDING_REFUND
API -> DB : Kembalikan kuota
API -> DB : INSERT notifikasi BOOKING_DIBATALKAN
DB --> API : OK
App --> Pelanggan : Notifikasi booking dibatalkan\n& refund sedang diproses

Staff -> Staff : Proses refund manual\n(transfer balik ke pelanggan)
Staff -> App : Update status refund → REFUNDED
App -> API : PATCH /internal/transaksi/{id}/refund
API -> DB : UPDATE transaksi status_refund = REFUNDED
API -> DB : INSERT notifikasi STATUS_REFUND
App --> Pelanggan : Notifikasi refund selesai

@enduml
